1. *Okolnosti* su uticale na našu odluku. (Circumstances influenced our decision.)
2. Ne mogu da predvidim sve *okolnosti*. (I can't predict all the circumstances.)
3. *Okolnosti* su se promenile od prošlog puta. (The circumstances have changed since last time.)
4. Moramo uzeti u obzir sve *okolnosti* pre nego donesemo odluku. (We need to take into account all circumstances before making a decision.)
5. *Okolnosti* su nam otežale posao. (Circumstances have made our job more difficult.)
6. U ovoj *okolnosti* je najbolje da se povučemo. (In this circumstance, it's best for us to withdraw.)
7. Bez obzira na *okolnosti*, moramo nastaviti dalje. (Regardless of the circumstances, we must continue forward.)
8. *Okolnosti* su se pokazale nepovoljnim za nas. (The circumstances have proved unfavorable for us.)
9. Nikada ne znaš koje će *okolnosti* uticati na tvoj život. (You never know what circumstances will impact your life.)
10. Sve *okolnosti* ukazuju na to da će biti kiše. (All circumstances point to there being rain.)